public class OutputDataset
extends org.ascape.model.event.DefaultScapeListener

Display output from a OutputDatasetProvider. When the scape stops after each run, adds an output data table node in the Navigator that displays the OutputDatasetProvider results in a table, and optionally outputs the results to a file. When the simulation finishes running, creates a multi run node if the OutputDatasetProvider is a MultiRunOutputDatasetProvider.
